documentation.text:
@title PoolAdvisory: The advisory pool contract (for advisors).
 @dev Follows a factory method to create vesting wallets for each new advisor

devdoc.details: Follows a factory method to create vesting wallets for each new advisor

params._cliffSeconds: The min time (cliff) before vested tokens can be redeemed
params._durationSeconds: The total vesting period for tokens

owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.

params._advisor: The beneficiary address representing the advisor
params._amount: The total amount of ZOR to vest for this advisor

renounceOwnership().details: Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions anymore. Can only be called by the current owner. NOTE: Renouncing ownership will leave the contract without an owner, thereby removing any functionality that is only available to the owner.

transferOwnership(address).details: Transfers ownership of the contract to a new account (`newOwner`). Can only be called by the current owner.

devdoc.title: PoolAdvisory: The advisory pool contract (for advisors).

registerAdvisor(address,uint256).notice: Registers a new advisor and creates a corresponding vesting wallet
